                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-medium text-[#2A2724] relative inline-block">
                        Filter & Sort
                        <svg class="absolute w-[110%] h-[15px] -bottom-2 -left-[5%] text-[#8B2626] opacity-80 overflow-visible" viewBox="0 0 100 10" fill="none" preserveAspectRatio="none">
